'''聖亞薩'''（{{lang-en|St Asaph}}，{{IPAc-en|s|ən|t|_|ˈ|æ|s|ə|f}}<ref>[http://phonetic-blog.blogspot.co.uk/2012/03/st-asaph.html St Asaph—John Wells's phonetic blog] {{Wayback|url=http://phonetic-blog.blogspot.co.uk/2012/03/st-asaph.html |date=20120618160617 }}, 15 March 2012. Retrieved 1 April 2012</ref>；{{lang-cy|Llanelwy}}，{{IPA-cy|ɬanˈɛlʊɨ̯|}}）是[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的一座城鎮<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-north-east-wales-17365580 BBC News—St Asaph in north Wales named Diamond Jubilee city] Retrieved 14 March 2012</ref>，位於[[登比郡|登比郡]]。據2011年人口普查，聖亞薩有人口3,355人<ref>[http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11128805&c=asaph&d=16&e=62&g=6489975&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1426290372312&enc=1 Office for National Statistics] {{Wayback|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11128805&c=asaph&d=16&e=62&g=6489975&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1426290372312&enc=1 |date=20150509095020 }} 2011 census - St. Asaph C</ref>，是英國人口第二少的擁有[[英國城市地位|城市地位]]的城鎮。
